{
  "stem": "24409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I then went to my office, and the girl told me there was somebody here from the police that you have to report to the police.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with the plan to tell all this, if possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I thought maybe, maybe it's just that I'm arrested like Turi was arrested, or like others were arrested.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I thought I would have to take a chance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have to go to the police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I could have been hiding at least for some time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the police kept me there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was formally introduced by a Austrian policeman who asked me if a few simple questions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have you ever had an affair with a gentile girl?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Have you ever sued a gentile for interest?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or have you ever taken interest for payment from [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "German? ?] Some of the crimes the Jews are supposed to have committed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I sit there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With me, two days was the interview.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not with me [INAUDIBLE], afterward, when I was still waiting outside for the formalities to be released.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For [INAUDIBLE], it was not release.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- yes, yes I know now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was sent down into the basement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was a school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was an emergency prison.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A prison for [INAUDIBLE], for they used this school in the Karajan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "K-A-R-A-J-A-N, Karajan, and it's strictly Jewish district.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Turi I know had been arrested the day before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the main thing for me now was to let the people know that I was not arrested because of the transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They should go on with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That rather I was arrested just as any other Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
